body: "\n# Seed Starting Notes\n\n- [technique] Pre-soak large seeds overnight before sowing #seeds (speeds germination)\n- [gotcha] Bottom heat dries the surface quickly (check twice daily)\n- [fact] Most warm-season crops germinate near twenty degrees Celsius #seeds\n- [requirement] Label every tray at sowing time #organization\n"
